metadata.name: eden
metadata.description:
As I opened my eyes, I was momentarily disoriented by the vibrant colors that surrounded me. It was as if I had been transported to a completely different world, a world where the sky was a deep shade of purple and the trees glowed with a golden light.

As I got to my feet, I realized that I felt different somehow. Lighter, more energized. And as I took my first steps, I noticed that my body moved with a grace and fluidity that I had never experienced before.

For the first time in my life, I knew that I was truly home. I had woken up on Eden, and nothing would ever be the same again.
